      *  TO THIS PROGRAM MAY ALSO APPLY TO FT0010.                    *                       CTI002
      *                                                               *
      *  Function:  This program will be called by all input          *
      *  programs which need to calculate an amount or verify         *
      *  an entered amount.                                           *
      *  (phase(s)) I/C                                               *
