      *  CHKDUP - Check for duplicate Currencies                      *
      *  DLVAM1 - Delivery Amount (First 2 Currencies)                *
      *  CHKDUP - Check for duplicate Currencies                      *
      *  DLVAM1 - Delivery Amount (Second 2 Currencies)               *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           DLVAMT    BEGSR
