      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  CHKDUP - If Currency is duplicated, the corresponding        *
      *           amounts (if non-zero) must be equal.                *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: DLVAMT                                            *
