      *  RETURN - Return control.                                     *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           CHKDUP    BEGSR
      *
      ** If both currencies are the same then so must be the amounts,
      ** otherwise it's an error.
      *
     C                     DO   2         X
     C           CCY,X     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           X         ADD  1         Z       10
     C           CCY,X     LOKUPCCY,Z                    06
     C           *IN06     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SELEC
     C           AMNT,X    WHEQ *ZERO
     C                     Z-ADDAMNT,Z    AMNT,X
     C           AMNT,Z    WHEQ *ZERO
     C                     Z-ADDAMNT,X    AMNT,Z
     C           AMNT,X    WHNE AMNT,Z
